OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FBreezier through Tuesday, with cloud
OL,7,Fbreaks developing ahead of overnight
OL,8,Frain. Wednesday, early rain clearing,
OL,9,Fthen brighter and blustery with
OL,10,Fscattered showers. Thursday, windy
OL,11,Fwith showers, perhaps more persistent
OL,12,Frain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
